<P>
GROUP HOSTS ANNUAL HOLIDAY BOUTIQUE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Laguna Village Homeowners Assn. will hold its annual holiday boutique today 
at the complex's clubhouse. 
</P>
<P>
The boutique, to be held from 9 a.m. to 4 p.m., will offer more than 75 booths 
selling arts, crafts and gifts. The clubhouse is at 23300 Santa Vittoria Drive 
in Laguna Hills. Some of the proceeds will go to help a needy family. 
</P>
</TEXT>
