<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: FULLERTON; 
</P>
<P>
DIRECTORS SOUGHT FOR CULTURAL CENTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The board of trustees of the Muckenthaler Cultural Center is accepting 
applications from people interested in serving on the center's board of 
directors. 
</P>
<P>
The application deadline is Dec. 14. Applicants are not required to be 
residents of Fullerton. 
</P>
<P>
The board is the chief support group for the cultural center and provides input 
and direction on programming. The board also sponsors various fund-raising 
programs to help support center activities. 
</P>
<P>
Applications can be obtained at the center, 1201 W. Malvern Ave., Fullerton. 
For more information, call (714) 738-6595. 
</P>
</TEXT>
